Hello Guys,
  Through this you can play pc games without using your hand means you don't have to worry about your mouse and keybord.
  You can play this game by just moving your body.

Guys you all are thinking how to open the game after running this code.

So, the basic steps you have to follow is:
    1) Open you browser
    2) Search the game which you want to play.
    3) And open the game and clap your hand your game will start automatically.
